  "text": "2.3. L 1 methods. During the last few years, the attention in high dimensional linear regression problems has shifted to l 1 penalized approaches that do not rely on least squares estimators. Some examples of such methods are: Lasso, LARS, Forward Stagewise [CITATION_1] ] and the Dantzig Selector [CITATION_2] ].",
